      "id": "PopularPost78928",
      "post_content": "In its day, at the common rarity, many thought Grizzly Bears were undercosted. The vanilla 2/2's in the other colors ([Gray Ogre](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gray Ogre), [Pearled Unicorn](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pearled Unicorn), [Scathe Zombies](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Scathe Zombies)) all had a converted mana cost of 3. But green was known for having better-than-average creatures, and the Grizzlies delivered. ",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost78928\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">In its day, at the common rarity, many thought Grizzly Bears were undercosted.  The vanilla 2/2's in the other colors (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Gray Ogre\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gray Ogre\">Gray Ogre</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pearled Unicorn\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pearled Unicorn\">Pearled Unicorn</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Scathe Zombies\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Scathe Zombies\">Scathe Zombies</a>) all had a converted mana cost of 3.  But green was known for having better-than-average creatures, and the Grizzlies delivered.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '78928'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (6/9/2010 8:50:24 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRat