    {
      "id": "PopularPost114313",
      "post_content": "One of the first creatures I ever cast. Just good, plain old Grizzly Bears like we have on Earth. They told me I was a noob (not that that term existed in 1994) who was not ready to throw dragons and demons around. But they were exciting to send into battle, even if I didn't understand combat math.  \nI will never accept Runeclaw Bear as a replacement. Grizzlies represent the simplest of creatures for beginners to enter into the game with. Flavor-wise, that is much more important than some nondes.cript magical claws. ",
      "posted_by": "GainsBanding",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost114313\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">One of the first creatures I ever cast.  Just good, plain old Grizzly Bears like we have on Earth.  They told me I was a noob (not that that term existed in 1994) who was not ready to throw dragons and demons around.  But they were exciting to send into battle, even if I didn't understand combat math.<br/>I will never accept Runeclaw Bear as a replacement.  Grizzlies represent the simplest of creatures for beginners to enter into the game with.  Flavor-wise, that is much more important than some nondes.cript magical claws.     </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '114313'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2974\">GainsBanding</span>\r\n                                (11/7/2010 12:21:50 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../